==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fauteuil
<hw>Fau`teuil"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>Faldistory</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An armchair; hence (because
the members sit in fauteuils or armchairs), membership in the French
Academy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Chair of a presiding officer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fautor</ent>⟦br⟧
